WEBVTT

00:05:28.704 --> 00:05:31.413
Shuning uchun biz bu qiyin haqiqatlarni

00:05:31.413 --> 00:05:34.163
zarur bo’lganda gapirishga
odatlanishimiz kerak.

00:05:34.829 --> 00:05:36.121
Va men --

00:05:36.163 --> 00:05:39.329
(Qarsaklar)

00:05:39.371 --> 00:05:43.079
Va men bu haqiqatlarni gapirishim 
kerakligini bilaman, chunki

00:05:43.121 --> 00:05:45.038
to’g’ri so’zlik men uchun 
juda muhim.

00:05:45.079 --> 00:05:47.329
Mening yaxlitligim men uchun aziz.

00:05:47.329 --> 00:05:49.871
Adolat - Men adolatni tanlov deb
hisoblamayman. Bizda

00:05:49.913 --> 00:05:51.371
doim adolat
bo’lishi kerak.

00:05:51.413 --> 00:05:54.746
Bundan tashqari, shea yog’iga asosiy 
qiymat sifatida ishonaman va -

00:05:54.788 --> 00:05:56.079
(Kulgi) 
nazarimda agar

00:05:56.079 --> 00:05:59.704
ko’proq o’zimizga qaraganimizda,
dunyo yaxshiroq bo’lar edi. Bular mening